We've agreed to honour, by gentleman's agreement, a rotation keeper.  I don't see why we can't do the same for an official list-keeper and dice-roller.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
