4. Camping Ragefire in Skyfire is unnecessary and gives no right to the spawn. However, the cleric must kill Ragefire within 24 hours of the spawn, or it goes FFA. This should allow clerics in all time zones to gather the forces necessary to make the kill.<br>
<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
