<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Divine Grace respects all recognized camps, and will not knowingly Kill Steal anybody.</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
That's it, thank you. I am not going out on a limb or speaking for people whom I should not be when I state this, I am simply reciting guild policy. As long as the server in general recognizes the SF Rage as a camp, DG respects it.<br>
<br>
Draelyn and Adarian are basically good people, believe it or not, if maybe a little excitable in debate. They can pontificate here if it entertains them, good for them. Heck, maybe even help form a new server policy on the mob, if they can tone it down some. But as they state plainly, they are not speaking for DG or relaying guild policy, but merely trying to add their thoughts to this debate. Just wanted to make that clear.<br>
<br>
